                  <section id="content" role="page content" aria-label="extension information">
                     			
                     			
                     				
                     
                        <h1>Arkansas Public Policy Center</h1>
                        
                        <p>The Public Policy Center exists to provide Arkansans with&nbsp;research-based information
                           and education about public issues. Public issues are defined as pressing and emerging
                           issues that involve multiple points of view and have widespread consequences.</p>
                        
                        <p><strong>Our goals are to:</strong></p>
                        
                        <ul>
                           
                           <li>Increase citizen knowledge, awareness and understanding of public issues</li>
                           
                           <li>Enhance public participation in decisions regarding public issues</li>
                           
                           <li>Help citizens craft, evaluate and implement alternative solutions to public issues</li>
                           </ul>
                        <!-- ou:migration_comment ORIGINAL TMPL CONTENT ENDS HERE -->
                        
