                                    <p><a class="noAfterIcon" title="Retail Beef Production Practices: A Survey of Beef Processing Capacity in Arkansas" href="/business-communities/public-policy-center/Arkansas-Beef-Council-Retail-Beef-Production-Report-May2020.pdf">Retail Beef Production Practices: A Survey of Beef Processing Capacity in Arkansas</a></p>
                                    
